stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> FormEmpty
    FormEmpty --> FormFilling : User starts typing
    FormFilling --> Validating : Submit clicked
    Validating --> ValidationError : Invalid fields
    ValidationError --> FormFilling : Fix errors
    Validating --> Submitting : All valid
    Submitting --> Success : 201 response
    Submitting --> ServerError : 400/500 response
    ServerError --> FormFilling : Fix and retry
    Success --> [*]